# =============================================================================
# Chain Registry Node — Inner Project .gitignore
# SECURITY: Never commit private keys, seed phrases, or credentials
# POLICY: Only source code and scripts are tracked.
#         No docs, models, packages, libraries, or generated artifacts.
# =============================================================================

# =============================================================================
# DOCUMENTATION — ignore generated/local notes; track operator-facing docs
# =============================================================================
*.md
!README.md
!DELIVERABLES_INDEX.md
!TESTNET_READINESS_REPORT.md
!DEEP_DIVE_ANALYSIS.md
!DOCKER.md
!docs/*.md
!testnet/README.md
!testnet/OPERATOR.md
!testnet/QUICKSTART.md
!testnet/gcp-public-hosting.md
!testnet/SOAK_TEST.md
!testnet/bootstrap/README.md
!testnet/spec-server/README.md
!hub/content/**/*.md

# =============================================================================
# DOCS DIRECTORY — public docs only (chain-registry-core)
# =============================================================================
docs/*
!docs/PUBLIC.md
!docs/PUBLIC_TESTNET_QUICKSTART.md
!docs/TESTNET_PHASE_SCOPE.md
!docs/WALLET_KEY_DERIVATION.md
!docs/DATABASE_SCHEMA.md
!docs/CREG_LIMITATIONS_PUBLIC_READINESS_PLAN.md
!docs/EXTERNAL_COPY_CHECKLIST.md
!docs/PUBLIC_COPY_REVIEW.md
!docs/SEC-401-AUDIT-SCOPE.md

# =============================================================================
# ENVIRONMENT & SECRETS (CRITICAL — NEVER COMMIT)
# =============================================================================
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
.env.backup.*
*.env
secrets/
*secret*
!testnet/gcp/_GcpSecret.ps1
# SEC-301b: hot-key loader crate (source only — not credential files)
!crates/secrets/
!crates/secrets/**
!.gitignore

