# Keep malicious-fixture package inputs: they are committed test inputs for
# crates/validator/tests/malicious_fixtures.rs, not scratch output. The broad
# `package/` rule above otherwise excludes them, which breaks the test in a
# fresh CI checkout ("<id> missing package/ directory").
!testnet/malicious-fixtures/*/package/
!testnet/malicious-fixtures/*/package/**

